One falsifiable sentence naming a **specific mechanism** (not "make it faster").

## Hypothesis Type

Exactly one of: **Performance** | **Correctness** | **Debt** | **Architecture**

## Confidence

Exactly one of: **High** | **Medium** | **Low**

Reasoning (optional Obsidian pattern cites under this repo’s `Forge/Projects/<ForgeProjectSlug>/` only).

